## Reshape to long format

One row = one (sample × sensor) observation.

```{r anova-reshape}
df_long <- df_wide %>%
  pivot_longer(
    cols = starts_with("cadence_"),
    names_to = "sensor",
    names_prefix = "cadence_",
    values_to = "cadence"
  ) %>%
  filter(!is.na(cadence)) %>%
  mutate(
    sensor     = factor(sensor, levels = c("LF", "RF", "LW", "RW", "SA")),
    patient_id = factor(patient_id),
    visit      = factor(visit),
    sample_id  = factor(sample_id),
